{"tid":1652572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜分享一個支那消息畀大家，激勵一下大家士氣，唔好放棄","createTime":"2019-10-13T17:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T23:18:53.000Z","uid":176282,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"002ce83bda04a2749705fe2c4f9259c757911788","tid":1652572,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"我唔知道有幾多人覺得呢場運動注定輸，覺得香港冇可能贏到中共<br />\n<br />\n我想講，今次其實全世界，包括支那自己都幫緊香港<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬我唔多講，NBA 暴雪之類大家都知<br />\n<br />\n大陸大家呢幾日講得最多係咩？品蔥，上海。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋反共係好正常，一個係反共論壇，一個係畀支那吸血嘅城市<br />\n<br />\n但係我想講，宜家支那宣揚民主主義，好有可能會反噬返佢自己。<br />\n<br />\n如果有關注開NBA戰線應該會知道，大陸戰狼係NBA呢件事先係由聲討Morey（全體抵制NBA），到HUPU等討論區封鎖討論（恥笑討論區為咗利益限制言論），到上海賽（恥笑上海人冇骨氣），到深圳賽（恥笑中國好多人冇骨氣）。<br />\n<br />\n到咗呢個階段，戰狼依然係認為中國NBAfans跪，唔係政府跪，即使政府唔畀戰狼帶國旗，帶banner入場（我都唔知戰狼係曲定直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n不過今日大陸重新轉播NBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，戰狼終於知道：屌，原來支那真係咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上言論開始變<br />\n<br />\nNGA討論區，大陸暴雪game討論區，但係因為大陸以前魔獸實在太hit，其實唔關暴雪事嘅分區都多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKb1N11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKb1N11.jpg&h=dca880e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHUPU，當然少不了大陸最大籃球討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhV6eHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhV6eHT.jpg&h=86121348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以見到，大陸嘅戰狼已經開始懷疑自己一生人一直信仰嘅國家民族節氣，咩骨氣，咩中國人站起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家支那係內憂內憂外患，點解要咁輕易放棄，點解要放過整個地球最邪惡嘅共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n我po出去我就會上床訓，朝早起個靚身，食個靚茶，返個靚工，然後七點同各位不見不散"},{"pid":"e58b10ffde7de7915cf297585f859c24fa37c848","tid":1652572,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6dba1408bffcfa77d10ba5cb8245c3171eb72c","tid":1652572,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HathylE/status/1183432493745049601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHathylE%2Fstatus%2F1183432493745049601&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=38c40cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHathylE%2Fstatus%2F1183432493745049601&h=e1778f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HathylE/status/1183432493745049601</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb3d4805d48d7f34d8262c00589e16585e5d95e","tid":1652572,"uid":48579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"點解你唔print screen要影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc08ddd38ba20ba7b33abd3c6f5aa438571d6143","tid":1652572,"uid":45400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">左膠 女人 我請你地唔好再講夠啦唔好打死人啦 唔好阻住手足！而家打仗呀 黑警畜蟲打我地d手足個時你地有無衝上前講唔好呀夠啦打夠啦打死人呀？你地淨係識跑！</span></span>"},{"pid":"695b03c1629d1410552c56e50116e62ef6c097d2","tid":1652572,"uid":322304,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:35:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"010edcc9933e5e18112eb4e7669642ac375e6a94","tid":1652572,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13e97e4d894590c43abda4d51902b8169db5517c","tid":1652572,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb3d4805d48d7f34d8262c00589e16585e5d95e","tid":1652572,"ui